yTime":"2021-04-18T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"咁自殺犯唔犯法？<br />\n教唆他人自殺又犯唔犯法？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:16:31.000Z","msg":"大律師黃宇逸回覆稱，若投白票本身不犯法，政府要將煽惑他人投白票「刑事化」便需要更強的理由。對於謝偉俊以自殺為例，<strong><span class=\"orange\">黃表示自殺在早年是刑事罪</span></strong>，後因政策原因才非刑事化，而教唆他人自殺在社會上不容許、不道德，間接使他人失去生命，故有刑事規範；煽惑他人投白票和自殺兩者不能相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n汁：明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20210415/s00001/1618424754519/%E8%AC%9D%E5%81%89%E4%BF%8A%E3%80%8C%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E3%80%8D%E5%96%BB%E3%80%8C%E7%B1%B2%E6%8A%95%E7%99%BD%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%8D-%E5%85%A9%E7%9A%86%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95-%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80-%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%97%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%B1%AC%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%A6%E8%AB%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210415%2Fs00001%2F1618424754519%2F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%2590%25B9%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2596%25BB%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E3%2580%258D-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%259A%2586%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E8%25AB%2596&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVprnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=79db49f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210415%2Fs00001%2F1618424754519%2F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%2590%25B9%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2596%25BB%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E3%2580%258D-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%259A%2586%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580-%25